{"type":null,"faqId":18685,"title":"添加/取消闹钟","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">时钟</span><span>，选择屏幕上放的“闹钟”页，进入闹钟界面。                 </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>选择屏幕左下角的</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62990\" style=\"width:0.68333334in;height:0.825in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">添加闹钟</span><span>，进入设置闹钟界面，可以进行如下操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击</span><span class=\"s1\">时间</span><span>，设置闹钟铃响的时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击</span><span class=\"s1\">重复</span><span>，选择需要闹钟重复的周期。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击</span><span class=\"s1\">铃声</span><span>，选择闹钟铃声。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>勾选</span><span class=\"s1\">振动</span><span>，设置手机在闹钟铃响时振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击</span><span class=\"s1\">标签，</span><span>输入闹钟时间名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击</span><span class=\"s1\">右上角对号</span><span>，完成闹钟的添加。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在闹钟主界面，当闹钟列表数较少时，可以直接看到当前所有闹钟的列表；当闹钟列表数较多时，可通过上下滑动的方式查看所有闹钟列表。在每条闹钟记录后面有开关按钮，向左滑动，按钮置灰，显示为关闭，就表示取消了这个闹钟。短按一条闹钟记录，弹出闹钟编辑界面，可对该条闹钟进行编辑修改以及删除闹钟等操作。长按一条闹钟记录， 弹出删除闹钟界面，在弹出的删除列表中， 点击对应闹钟项的红色删除图标，完成删除。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1749","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422260330000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,CherryPlus-TL00,CherryPlus-TL00H,CherryPlus-TL00M,CherryPlus-TL10,CherryPlus-UL00,CherryPlus-UL10","visitedTimes":17,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}